  "parent": "经典问题",
  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "What？",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "求 $\\sum_{l=1}^n \\sum_{r=l}^n f(l, r)$",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "How?",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "<a href=\"/tags\" class=\"tag-link\">#贡献法</a>",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>核心思想</strong>：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "不要去想 “每个子段的答案是多少” ，而是想 <strong>“某个元素在多少个子段中做出了贡献”</strong>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>公式</strong>：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ \\text{Total Ans} = \\sum_{i} (\\text{Value}_i \\times \\text{Count}_i) $$",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>经典例题</strong>：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>所有子段的最小值之和</strong>：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "对于每个 $a_i$，找到它左边第一个比它小的位置 $L_i$ 和右边第一个比它小的位置 $R_i$（使用<strong>单调栈</strong>）。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$a_i$ 作为最小值的子段范围是 $(L_i, R_i)$。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "贡献 $= a_i \\times (i - L_i) \\times (R_i - i)$。",
              "depth": 3
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "当然，并非所有题都得用贡献法",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "如： <a href=\"/p/mc0472-郭嘉破阵\" class=\"wikilink\">MC0472 郭嘉破阵</a>",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
